Insurance

Property Quote Business Process

We've created a quote business process for Homeowners and Renters insurance. You can create new quotes from:

OmniScript flow

Quote object UI

Policyholder Site

Create Quote from Account: Quickly create an Auto, Marine or Property quote from the account page with just a few clicks.

Quote Proposal OmniScript: Create quote documents for lines of business that need them.

Property Quote OmniScript: Look under the hood of the property insurance quote process.
Property Quote UI: Follow a user-friendly workflow and create a quote from the Lex console.
Property Quote from Policyholder Site: Policyholders can follow a guided flow to quickly create quotes for property insurance.
